headline: Match Group to Present at the Barclays Global Technology Conference
summary: Match Group (NASDAQ: MTCH) announced today that Steven Bailey, Chief Financial Officer of Match Group, will participate in a fireside chat at the Barclays Global Technology Conference on Thursday, December 11 at 2:00 p.m. Eastern Time (ET). A live webcast and replay of the fireside chat will be available at https://ir.mtch.com/investor-relations/news-events/news-events/.

headline: 1 Small-Cap Stock to Research Further and 2 Facing Headwinds
summary: Investors looking for hidden gems should keep an eye on small-cap stocks because they’re frequently overlooked by Wall Street. Many opportunities exist in this part of the market, but it is also a high-risk, high-reward environment due to the lack of reliable analyst price targets.
